<style>{{{money_claim_doc_css}}}</style>
<h1>Particulars of Claim</h1>

<p><strong>Claimant:</strong> {{claimant_display_name}}</p>
<p><strong>Defendant:</strong> {{defendant_display_name}}</p>
<p><strong>Property:</strong> {{#if property_full_address}}{{property_full_address}}{{else}}{{property_address}}{{#if property_postcode}}, {{property_postcode}}{{/if}}{{/if}}</p>

<h2>Parties and tenancy</h2>
<p>
  The Claimant is the landlord of the property. The Defendant is, or was, the tenant of the property under a
  periodic tenancy agreement that commenced on {{tenancy_start_date}}.
</p>
<p>
  Under the tenancy agreement the Defendant was required to pay rent of {{currency rent_amount}} {{rent_frequency}}{{#if payment_day}},
  in advance on the {{payment_day}}{{ordinal_suffix payment_day}} day of each rent period{{/if}}. The Claimant relies on those
  tenancy terms as the contractual basis for the sums claimed.
</p>
{{#if particulars_of_claim}}
<p>
  The Claimant has also recorded the following case summary: {{particulars_of_claim}}
</p>
{{/if}}

<h2>Breach and rent arrears</h2>
<p>
  The Defendant failed to pay rent as it fell due. As at {{generation_date}}, the rent arrears claimed total
  {{currency arrears_total}}.
</p>
<p>
  {{#if arrears_schedule_is_summary}}
  The attached schedule records the total arrears figure entered by the Claimant. Before filing, the Claimant
  should attach or check the rent ledger, rent statement, bank records, or other documents showing how the
  figure is made up.
  {{else}}
  A detailed schedule is attached and marked "Schedule of Rent Arrears". It sets out the rent periods, the
  rent due, the amount paid, and the running balance relied on for the claim.
  {{/if}}
</p>
<p>
  The Claimant says the Defendant has had the benefit of the tenancy but has not paid the outstanding sums.
  The non-payment is relied on as a breach of the rent payment terms of the tenancy agreement.
</p>

{{#if damage_items.length}}
<h2>Property damage and other sums</h2>
<p>The Claimant also says the Defendant is liable for damage beyond fair wear and tear. The amounts claimed are:</p>
<ul>
  {{#each damage_items}}
  <li>{{description}} - {{currency amount}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

{{#if other_charges.length}}
{{#unless damage_items.length}}<h2>Property damage and other sums</h2>{{/unless}}
<p>The Claimant also seeks the following recoverable sums arising from the tenancy:</p>
<ul>
  {{#each other_charges}}
  <li>{{description}} - {{currency amount}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ul>
{{/if}}

{{#if pre_action_summary}}
<h2>Pre-action position</h2>
<p>
  Before preparing the claim, the Claimant recorded the following pre-action steps: {{pre_action_summary}}
</p>
<p>
  The Claimant says the debt remains unpaid and that court action is now required unless the Defendant pays
  the sum claimed or raises a properly evidenced dispute.
</p>
{{/if}}

{{#if has_evidence_reliance_items}}
<h2>Evidence relied on</h2>
<p>
  The Claimant says the following evidence is available or should be attached to support the claim:
</p>
<ol>
  {{#each evidence_reliance_items}}
  <li><strong>{{label}}:</strong> {{detail}}</li>
  {{/each}}
</ol>
{{else}}
{{#if evidence_summary}}
<h2>Evidence relied on</h2>
<p>{{evidence_summary}}</p>
{{/if}}
{{/if}}

{{#if claim_interest}}
<h2>Interest</h2>
<p>
  The Claimant claims interest pursuant to section 69 County Courts Act 1984 at {{interest_rate}}% per annum
  from {{interest_start_date}} to {{generation_date}}, calculated at {{currency interest_to_date}}, and continuing at
  {{currency daily_interest}} per day until judgment or earlier payment.
</p>
{{/if}}

<h2>Relief sought</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Principal debt claimed totalling {{currency total_claim_amount}}</li>
  <li>Court fee of {{currency court_fee}}</li>
  {{#if solicitor_costs}}
  <li>Fixed legal costs of {{currency solicitor_costs}}</li>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if claim_interest}}
  <li>Interest under section 69 CCA 1984</li>
  {{/if}}
</ol>
<p>
  The Claimant asks the court to enter judgment for those sums{{#if claim_interest}} and for continuing daily
  interest claimed until judgment or earlier payment{{/if}}.
</p>

<h2>Statement of truth</h2>
<p>
  I believe that the facts stated in these particulars of claim are true.
</p>
<p>Signed: _________________________ ({{signatory_name}})</p>
<p>Dated: _________________________ {{#if signature_date}}({{signature_date}}){{else}}(To be signed and dated before filing){{/if}}</p>
<p><em><strong>Important:</strong> This document must be signed and dated by the claimant or their legal representative before filing with the court.</em></p>
